\left\lceil\frac{n}{2^k}\right\rceil = \left\lceil\frac{\left\lceil\frac{n}{2^{k-1}}\right\rceil}{2}\right\rceil
\left\lceil\frac{n}{2^{k+1}}\right\rceil = \left\lceil\frac{\left\lceil\frac{n}{2^k}\right\rceil}{2}\right\rceil
x = \left\lceil\frac{n}{2^{k+1}}\right\rceil
x-1 \lt \frac{n}{2^{k+1}} \le x
